Diamond::
She watches his eyes look at her wrist. She puts her hand behind her 
back."Fine. Just fine."

She realised he saw the wires and feels angry with herself for being 
careless.

She sees him put the cuffs in the machine. "Ah, would you mind just 
throwing those things away. You won't learn anything from them."

and
